Hi all — everything is working in the block below except for `&lt;p&gt; {{ content.post_list_content|truncatehtml(100) }}&lt;/p&gt;` do I have something marked up wrong?

```                    {% for content in contents %}

                    &lt;div class="cell medium-4"&gt;
                        &lt;div class="c-post-card orange-card"&gt;
                            &lt;div class="c-post-card-body"&gt;
                                {% if content.topic_list %}
                                {% for topic in content.topic_list %}
                                &lt;a href="#" class="c-post-card-tag"&gt;{{ topic.name }}&lt;/a&gt; 
                              {% endfor %}
                              {% endif %}
                                &lt;h5&gt;{{ content.name }}&lt;/h5&gt;
                                &lt;p&gt; {{ content.post_list_content|truncatehtml(100) }}&lt;/p&gt;
                            &lt;/div&gt;
                            &lt;div class="c-post-card-footer"&gt;
                                &lt;a href="{{ content.absolute_url }}"&gt;Learn More&lt;/a&gt;
                            &lt;/div&gt;
                        &lt;/div&gt;
                    &lt;/div&gt;

                    {% endfor %}```
